quran[11{c,v,t}:
17,76,aur yeh log is baat par bhi taley rahay hain ke tumahray qadam iss sir zameen se ukhaar den aur tumhe yahan se nikaal bahar karen lekin agar yeh aisa karen ge to tumahray baad yeh khud yahan kuch ziyada der nah tehr saken ge
17,77,"yeh hamara mustaqil tareeq car hai jo unn sab Rasolo-n ke muamlay mein hum ne brta hai jahin tum se pehlay hum ne bheja tha, aur hamaray tareeq car mein tum koi tagayur nah pao ge"
17,78,namaz qaim karo zawaal aftaab se le kar andheray taq aur Fajar ke quran ka bhi iltazam karo kyunkay quran Fajar Mashhood hota hai
17,79,"aur raat ko t_hjd parho, yeh tumahray liye Nafil hai, baeed nahi ke tumhara rab tumhe maqam Mahmood par Faiz kar day"
17,80,"aur dua karo ke parvar-digaar, mujh ko jahan bhi to le ja sachaai ke sath le ja aur jahan se bhi nikaal sachaai ke sath nikaal aur apni taraf se aik Iqtidaar ko mera madadgaar bana day"
17,81,"aur elaan kar do ke"" haq aa gaya aur baatil mit gaya, baatil to mitne hi wala hai """
17,82,"hum iss quran ke silsila Tanzil mein woh kuch nazil kar rahay hain jo maan-ne walon ke liye to Shifa aur rehmat hai, magar zaalmon ke liye khasaray ke siwa aur kisi cheez mein izafah nahi karta"
17,83,"ensaan ka haal yeh hai ke jab hum is ko Nemat ataa karte hain to woh inthtaaur peeth mourr laita hai, aur jab zara museebat se do chaar hota hai to mayoos honay lagta hai"
17,84,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un logon se keh do ke"" har aik apne tareeqay par amal kar raha hai, ab yeh tumhara rab hi behtar jaanta hai ke seedhi raah par kon hai """
17,85,"yeh log tum se rooh ke mutaliq puchhte hain kaho"" yeh rooh mere rab ke hukum se aati hai, magar tum logon ne ilm se kam hi behra paaya hai """
17,86,"aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum chahain to woh sab kuch tum se chean len jo hum ne wahi ke zareya se tum ko ataa kya hai, phir tum hamaray muqablay mein koi himayati nah pao ge jo usay wapas dila sakay"
